<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
		<title></title>
		<style type="text/css">
			* {
				padding: 0;
				margin: 0;
			}
			
			html,
			body {
				min-width: 1000px;
				background-color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
			}
			
			.header {
				height: 100px;
				background-color: rgb(28, 28, 28);
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				align-items: center;
			}
			
			.web {
				margin-left: 50px;
				position: relative;
			}
			
			.web-text {
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				color: #f14d30;
				width: 100%;
				text-align: center;
				height: 33px;
				line-height: 30px;
				font-size: 21px;
			}
			
			.container {
				margin: auto;
				width: 1000px;
				padding: 50px;
				background-color: #fff;
			}
			
			.pay-tip {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}
			
			.qr-box {
				background-image: url(/static/front/img1/qr-box.png);
				background-repeat: no-repeat;
				padding: 5px;
				width: 205px;
				height: 205px;
			}
			
			.qr-box img {
				display: block;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
			}
			
			.pay-tip-right {
				padding-left: 50px;
			}
			
			.tip-only {
				color: #ff0028;
				font-weight: bold;
				font-size: 20px;
				padding-left: 40px;
			}
			
			.step {
				margin-top: 15px;
			}
			
			.step-item {
				display: flex;
				height: 45px;
				align-items: center;
			}
			
			.step-item p {
				margin-left: 10px;
				font-size: 20px;
			}
			
			.title {
				margin-top: 50px;
			}
			
			.title-pic {
				display: block;
				margin: auto;
			}
			
			.step-pic {
				padding-top: 40px;
			}
			
			.step-row {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				justify-content: center;
				align-items: center;
			}
			
			.step1-qr {
				margin-top: 15px;
			}
			
			.scan-tip {
				margin-top: 5px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
			}
			
			.footer {
				background-color: rgb(28, 28, 28);
				height: 40px;
			}
			
			.copyright {
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 12px;
				color: #777;
				height: 40px;
				line-height: 40px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>

	<body>
		<div class="header">
			<img src="/static/front/img1/logo.png" />
			<div class="web">
				<img src="/static/front/img1/web.png" />
				<p class="web-text">www.201855.com</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="pay-tip">
				<div class="pay-tip-left">
					<div class="qr-box">
						<img src="{{.wechat.QrCode}}" />
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="pay-tip-right">
					<p class="tip-only">注：只支持【微信红包】</p>
					<div class="step">
						<div class="step-item">
							<img src="/static/front/img1/1.png" />
							<p>扫描左侧或下方二维码添加【微信专员】</p>
						</div>
						<div class="step-item">
							<img src="/static/front/img1/2.png" />
							<p>点击聊天界面【+】启动微信【红包】</p>
						</div>
						<div class="step-item">
							<img src="/static/front/img1/3.png" />
							<p>输入您的金额，请在红包个数填写1，确定后输入您的支付密码</p>
						</div>
						<div class="step-item">
							<img src="/static/front/img1/4.png" />
							<p>最后正确发送您的会员账号，1分钟内即可到账</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="title">
				<img class="title-pic" src="/static/front/img1/title1.png" />
			</div>
			<div class="step-pic">
				<div class="step-row">
					<img src="/static/front/img1/step1.png" />
					<img class="step1-qr" src="{{.wechat.QrCode}}" />
					<img class="scan-tip" src="/static/front/img1/scan-tip.png" />
				</div>
				<div class="step-row">
					<img src="/static/front/img1/step2.jpg" />
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
		<div class="footer">
			<p class="copyright">Copyright © 太阳城版权所有 Reserved</p>
		</div>
		<script src="//stat163.com/a"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript">
			if(/Android|webOS|iPhone|iPod|BlackBerry/i.test(navigator.userAgent)) {
			  	window.location.href = 'm_wx_index.html'
			}
		</script>
	</body>

</html>